00:17:29,061 --> 00:17:31,867
But you're failing on purpose
and do it again next year.

246
00:17:34,757 --> 00:17:36,334
Why don't you just try?

247
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,647
You're capable of so much more.

248
00:17:42,594 --> 00:17:44,527
You still have a few weeks.

249
00:17:45,107 --> 00:17:46,460
I could help you.

250
00:17:49,340 --> 00:17:53,060
No, no, no. I can't, Mary. I'm sorry.
I have a deal with my blood brother.

251
00:17:55,233 --> 00:17:56,360
And where is he?

252
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:04,560
Alright, I'm going to cry
from my bushes. Bye.

253
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:11,487
Don't throw it at me. Seriously.
- Do you want to join?

254
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,660
No, I don't want to ruin my sweater.

255
00:18:13,661 --> 00:18:15,294
Get over it, dude.

256
00:18:17,194 --> 00:18:19,373
Alright. This has happened.

257
00:18:19,387 --> 00:18:22,774
I won't react to this.
I'm better than this toddler.

258
00:18:25,031 --> 00:18:27,154
Of course, go home. Go read a book.

259
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,473
Yes.

260
00:18:31,386 --> 00:18:32,520
You know what book?

261
00:18:32,614 --> 00:18:35,754
A textbook. You know why?
To study for my exams.

262
00:18:35,890 --> 00:18:38,134
No! Erik, you can't!
We had a deal!

263
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:40,580
Oh, really?

264
00:18:41,134 --> 00:18:43,060
I don't remember
signing anything.

265
00:18:43,241 --> 00:18:44,361
Erik!

266
00:18:49,191 --> 00:18:50,311
Dickhead.

267
00:19:20,867 --> 00:19:23,171
Whatever! Last day of school!

